_:N0fdd333d22534e469235e2eec58da110 <http://schema.org/description> "The Office for Investment (OfI) is a joint unit of HM Treasury, the Department for Business and Trade, and the Prime Minister’s Office, 10 Downing Street. We source and secure transformational investment to drive growth, job creation, and increased productivity across the UK. Office for Investment is part of the Department for Business and Trade ." .
